Symbol.Script_3D:
! Contact person: <SzL, NJ>
! ============================================================================= ! GS Door Opening Functions ! =============================================================================
call "GS Door Opening Functions", parameters all iWindowShape = iWindowShape, openingArchHeight = openingArchHeight, nArchResolution = gs_res, bParalellInCurvedWalls = bParalellInCurvedWalls
! ============================================================================= ! Preview in Door Settings Dialog and in Listing ! =============================================================================
pen WALL_VIEW_PEN resol gs_res
if (GLOB_PREVIEW_MODE = 1 | GLOB_PREVIEW_MODE = 3) | GLOB_FEEDBACK_MODE then if not(WIDO_REVEAL_SIDE) then addz -WIDO_SILL else addz WIDO_SILL - WALL_THICKNESS + WIDO_FRAME_THICKNESS endif
cprism_ WALL_MAT_A, WALL_MAT_B, WALL_MAT_EDGE, 15, WALL_THICKNESS, A/2+0.2, -0.2, 8, A/2+0.2, B+0.2, 8, -A/2-0.2, B+0.2, 8, -A/2-0.2, -0.2, 8, A/2+0.2, -0.2, -1,
A/2, B-openingArchHeight, 79, A/2-R, B-openingArchHeight, 900, 0, asn(openingArchHeight/R), 4079, 0, B+EPS, 79, R-A/2, B-openingArchHeight, 900, 0, asn(openingArchHeight/R), 4079, -A/2, B-openingArchHeight, 79, -A/2, 0, 15, A/2, 0, 15, A/2, B-openingArchHeight, -1
del 1
end endif
if (GLOB_PREVIEW_MODE = 2) then ! IS but not surface extrude 10, 0, 0, WALL_THICKNESS, 16+32, A/2, B-openingArchHeight, 1, A/2-R, B-openingArchHeight, 900, 0, asn(openingArchHeight/R), 4001, 0, B+EPS, 1, R-A/2, B-openingArchHeight, 900, 0, asn(openingArchHeight/R), 4001, -A/2, B-openingArchHeight, 1, -A/2, 0, 0, A/2, 0, 0, A/2, B-openingArchHeight, -1 end endif
! ============================================================================= ! Hotspots ! =============================================================================
if abs(WIDO_ORIG_DIST) < EPS then del top if WIDO_REVEAL_SIDE then addz WIDO_FRAME_THICKNESS else mulz -1 endif addz WIDO_SILL
unID = 1
hotspot 0, B, 0,unID hotspot A/2,B-openingArchHeight, 0,unID+1 hotspot -A/2,B-openingArchHeight, 0,unID+2 unID = unID + 3
hotspot 0, B, -WALL_THICKNESS,unID hotspot A/2,B-openingArchHeight, -WALL_THICKNESS,unID+1 hotspot -A/2,B-openingArchHeight, -WALL_THICKNESS,unID+2 unID = unID + 3
del 2 endif
Symbol.Script_2D:
! Contact person: <SzL, NJ>
! ============================================================================= ! GS Door Opening Functions ! =============================================================================
call "GS Door Opening Functions", parameters all iWindowShape = iWindowShape, bParalellInCurvedWalls = bParalellInCurvedWalls
! =============================================================================
if not(gs_center_hpts_compatibility) then unID = 1 hotspot2 0,0, unID unID = unID + 1 endif
! ============================================================================= ! Arc in 2D - Straight Wall ! =============================================================================
if gs_arc_2D then line_type gs_brickw_lt toler 0.001
if WIDO_REVEAL_SIDE then mul2 1, -1 endif add2 0, WIDO_SILL
mul2 1, -1 add2 0, -B + openingArchHeight poly2_ 5,1, A/2, B - openingArchHeight, 1, A/2 - R, B - openingArchHeight, 900, 0, -asn(openingArchHeight/R), 4001, R - A/2, B - openingArchHeight, 900, 0, -asn(openingArchHeight/R), 4001 del 2
del 1 + WIDO_REVEAL_SIDE endif
Symbol.Script_1D:
! const values for parameter: iTypeCurvedWallCut CUT_PARALLEL = 1 CUT_RADIAL = 2
! Contact person: <SzL, NJ>
if GLOB_SCRIPT_TYPE = 7 | GLOB_SCRIPT_TYPE = 8 then goto "MasterEnd" ! forward migration, backward migration
! ============================================================================= ! Main Definitions ! =============================================================================
EPS = 0.0001
iWindowShape = 13 ! SHAPE_GOTHICARCH bParalellInCurvedWalls = (iTypeCurvedWallCut = CUT_PARALLEL)
! =============================================================================
R = (openingArchHeight^2)/A + A/4
"MasterEnd":
Symbol.Script_VL:
! Contact person: <SzL, NJ>
aaa = GLOB_ELEVATION ! #92488
! ============================================================================= ! GS Door Opening Functions ! =============================================================================
call "GS Door Opening Functions", parameters all iWindowShape = iWindowShape, bParalellInCurvedWalls = bParalellInCurvedWalls
! ============================================================================= ! Orientation ! =============================================================================
ac_OpeningSide = "" parameters ac_OpeningSide = ac_OpeningSide
! IFC Parameters -------------------------------------------------------------- call "IFC_optype_door" parameters all
values "A" range (0, ) values "B" range (0, ) values "openingArchHeight" range [A/2, B]
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_shoulder_height" then openingArchHeight = B - gs_shoulder_height parameters openingArchHeight = openingArchHeight else gs_shoulder_height = B - openingArchHeight parameters gs_shoulder_height = gs_shoulder_height endif
values{2} "iTypeCurvedWallCut" CUT_PARALLEL, `Параллельно`, CUT_RADIAL, `Радиально` values "gs_res" range[3,) values "gs_frame_thk" range[0,]
parameters gs_fontsize = abs(gs_fontsize) values "gs_fontsize" range(0,]
! Wall Contour Left/Right -----------------------------------------------------
gs_stack_right = not(gs_stack_right_contour) parameters gs_stack_right = not(gs_stack_right_contour)
gs_stack_left = not(gs_stack_left_contour) parameters gs_stack_left = not(gs_stack_left_contour)
!**************** Swedish list parameter control ********************** if gs_SWE_listParams_contr > 0 then call "SWE_ListParameters_control" parameters gs_SWE_listParams_contr = gs_SWE_listParams_contr, swe_list_d1 = swe_list_d1 endif
! ============================================================================= ! Zone Recognitions for Doors - Parapet wall Inset value calculation ! at Empty Openings: ! GLOB_ELEVATION - conditional - Zona`s flowing only at zero sill ! WIDO_REVEAL_SIDE - UNconditional - its always flipped inside WIDO_REVEAL_SIDE = 1 ! REVEAL (WIDO_SILL) - conditional - like its flipped outside (design) ! =============================================================================
ZONE_RECOGNITION_NONE = 0 ZONE_RECOGNITION_FULL = 1 ZONE_RECOGNITION_OUTSIDE = 2 ZONE_RECOGNITION_INSIDE = 3
if WIDO_REVEAL_SIDE then pwi = ZONE_RECOGNITION_INSIDE else pwi = ZONE_RECOGNITION_OUTSIDE endif
parameters pwi = pwi
